    "title": "Now Hiring Store Manager at Westside Capital India",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Westside Capital India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Store Manager to strengthen our Jabalpur-based team.\n\nAbout Westside Capital India:\nWestside Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Westside Capital India!",
